      "message": "Patch Set 7: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(7 inline comments)\n\nI propose splitting this up into two separate patches, or improving the commit message by detailing which parts of the code are removed altogether.\n\nAs it stands now, the commit message sounds like we only are touching the build system, but looking at some the of large code blocks removed, that isn't the case.\n\nSo something like \"this patch removes dead code from X, Y, and Z locations\" would be OK, but still prefer two patches.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
